headline: Kinder Morgan share price weakness a buying opportunity, says Argus
summary: Kinder Morgan’s (KMI) recent share price weakness create a buying opportunity, Argus analyst Bill Selesky tells investors in a research note. The firm, which has a Buy rating and $36 price target on the shares, believes that recent projects and recent acquisitions will be accretive to current earnings and generate higher near-term profit growth.
